          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只因刘皇叔，为报关羽之仇，被大都督陆逊火烧连营，在白帝城丧命了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你在怎讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在白帝城丧命了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙尚香昏倒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤妹醒来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听说是汉皇叔白帝丧命，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "皇叔，我夫，唉，喂呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "好一似万把刀刺在我心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "哭头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "皇叔哇！啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "撇下了未亡人何以为情？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄长啊！皇叔已死，我有意回转西川，前去奔丧吊祭，不知兄长意下如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "可叹你为报仇反送性命、孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，怎么你要人川奔丧吊祭么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫妻一场，理应如此，贤妹速速准备。待为兄派兵护送贤妹入川奔丧就是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢兄长。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "愚兄告辞了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙权",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "想人生必须要礼义为本，\n为江山那顾得手足之情。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙权下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴婢参见郡主。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "进宫何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀郡主：奴婢有话不知当讲不当讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有话快些讲来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "方才银安殿上，吕范定计：借郡主入川奔丧吊祭为名，主公统领大兵，明为护\n送，暗则夺取西川，那时灵堂变成战场，郡主可要留心一二啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙尚香惊慌。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这……我来问你，可是真情？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴婢亲耳听见，不敢慌报。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "起过了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀且住，想当年只为荆州九郡，将我用作美人之计，得配皇叔；如今皇叔已\n死，又要借我奔丧吊祭为名，夺取西川，两地军民岂不又遭涂炭，这便如何是\n好！有了，我不免假意去往江边祭奠，投江一死，免得再被兄长陷害了。\n内待过来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴婢在。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "速备祭礼，江边伺候。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我去到后宫，辞别母后便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "侍儿们备素服随我祭奠，\n到后宫别母后再去江边。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙尚香下。）"
        }
      ],
